{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1N001597", "chronotag": "1757948613255", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "1597", "numeroOrdreDepot": "1597", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17BTC1364", "triAmendement": "akaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaabobi", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA642847", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845425", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Bazin"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 2", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 2", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 2", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1364.asp#D_Article_2"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "3", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 3"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I.&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;&#x00C0;&nbsp;l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;3,&nbsp;apr&#x00E8;s le mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;aide&nbsp;&#x00BB;,</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ins&#x00E9;rer&nbsp;le mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;active&nbsp;&#x00BB;.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">II.&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;En cons&#x00E9;quence, &#x00E0; l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;6,&nbsp;apr&#x00E8;s le mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;aide&nbsp;&#x00BB;,</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ins&#x00E9;rer&nbsp;le mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;active&nbsp;&#x00BB;.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">III.&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;En cons&#x00E9;quence, &#x00E0; l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;7,&nbsp;apr&#x00E8;s le mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;aide&nbsp;&#x00BB;,</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">ins&#x00E9;rer&nbsp;le mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;active&nbsp;&#x00BB;.&nbsp;</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Amendement de repli.&nbsp;</p><p>Pour clarifier le dispositif d'\"aide &#x00E0; mourir\", il convient de bien nommer les choses. Or, le Conseil &#x00E9;conomique, social et environnemental (CESE) ou encore le Comit&#x00E9; consultatif national d&#x2019;&#x00E9;thique (CCNE) utilisent le terme &#x00AB; aide active &#x00E0; mourir &#x00BB;, ainsi que d'autres pays comme le Canada.&nbsp;</p><p>La clarification s&#x00E9;mantique semble d'autant plus importante que, d'une certaine mani&#x00E8;re, les soignants de soins palliatifs, en pratique et tr&#x00E8;s concr&#x00E8;tement, sont d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; des \"aidants &#x00E0; mourir\" en ce qu'ils accompagnent les derniers jours d'une vie.&nbsp;</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-05-09", "datePublication": "2025-05-19", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Rejet\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2025-05-17T10:32:32+02:00", "sort": "Rejet\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1N001597?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": "RUANR5L17S2025IDS29507", "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "1", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"idDiscussion": "30738", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "78576", "typePosition": "Dernier"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}